A '''Sern Prime topknot''' was a hairstyle from [[Sern Prime/Legends|Sern Prime]] that consisted of long hair gathered at the top of the head. Sern Prime's [[Senator/Legends|senator]], [[Fang Zar/Legends|Fang Zar]], had such a topknot.

